doc.after: LAN became the launch customer for the Pratt & Whitney PW6000 engine on the Airbus A318.[20] Its Airbus A319s and Airbus A320s are equipped with International Aero Engines V2500s. Lan Airlines has recently renovated its Boeing 767s, adding amenities like flat bed seats in Premium Business class, which offers 180 degrees of recline, and new touch screen personal TVs with on-demand content.[21]
